article_id:983,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Limited-Time Event, A Sweeping Retrospective, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/94df26266ed1c2a5fed58efdae01e510.png,message:<div>A new limited-time event, A Sweeping Retrospective, will start at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577340000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>During the A Sweeping Retrospective event, you can play the event-exclusive quests to get drop rewards and complete endeavors. Help Cleo with a major cleanup and see how all the residents of the Halidom are spending their time as this year draws to a close!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/94df26266ed1c2a5fed58efdae01e510.png"></div><div><br></div><div>It&#39;s the end of the year and Cleo is leading the charge to give the Halidom a much needed deep clean, but something is amiss and groups of fiends are appearing in the castle! Help the allies who joined this year and wipe the floor with the intruding fiends!</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div>3. There will not be a period after the A Sweeping Retrospective event has ended when you can still read the story.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1577250000,update_time1577250581